-- Guaranty Trust Bank Gets $100 Million Credit From African Development Bank
-- Ana Monteiro
-- 2010-06-23T13:58:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/guaranty-trust-bank-gets-100-million-credit-from-african-development-bank.html

          
          
             Guaranty Trust Bank Plc, a Nigerian
lender, received a $100 million line of credit from the African
Development Bank to fund projects in the West African nation.  
 The lender plans to fund projects in the oil, manufacturing
and transport industries, the African Development Bank said in
an e-mailed statement from Tunis. The facility is in addition to
credit provided to Guaranty in May 2006.  
          
          


  


        